Mandarin tones and voicing

2022-06-28

Run Praat script

speakr::praat_run("./code/cmn.praat")

Read the data table

cmn <- read_csv("data/derived/cmn.csv") %>%
  mutate(
    cq = degg_min_rel - degg_max_rel,
    f0 = 1000/period_dur,
    norm_time = (egg_min_1 - int_start) / (int_end - int_start),
    tone = str_sub(word, 3),
    c1 = str_sub(word, 1, 1)
  ) %>%
  filter(
    f0 < 400,
    cq > 0 & cq < 1
  )
## Rows: 4003 Columns: 11

Plot f0

cmn %>%
  ggplot(aes(norm_time, f0, colour = tone)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.2) +
  geom_smooth(method = "gam", formula = y ~ s(x, k = 4)) +
  facet_grid(~ c1) +
  scale_color_brewer(palette = "Dark2")

Plot CQ

cmn %>%
  ggplot(aes(norm_time, cq, colour = tone)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.2) +
  geom_smooth(method = "gam", formula = y ~ s(x, k = 4)) +
  facet_grid(~ c1) +
  scale_color_brewer(palette = "Dark2")
